description: Sometimes, life can be incredibly hard and unfair. This boy spent most of his early years in an orphanage. When he turned 18, he was basically kicked out into real life without any support. Fortunately, he had some unfinished high school education involving computers. I found him putting up posters advertising his starting business as a computer repair guy. When he told me his life story, including some very private stuff, I knew I had to help the poor boy at least a little. He responded almost too well, he was genuinely grateful. I felt kind of bad, because I had my dirty objective on my mind all the time. He looked extremely cute and I wanted him so badly. We found a beautiful spot in a forest where I could finally enjoy all his tight innocent holes.
title: Czech Hunter 249
